data.description: Why wait for new construction?  Over 100k in upgrade, this house has it all. Finished Basement with upper and lower Deck. Absolutely stunning interior with lots of attention to detail.  5 Bedrooms and 3.5 Baths. Open floor plan with double decks and patio that backs to woods. A gourmet kitchen that has custom cabinets and ceramic backsplash, stainless steel appliances, pot filler, oil rubbed bronze handles, brushed gold ceiling fan with remote , double oven microwave and a walk-in pantry.  The main level opens to a tiled deck that runs the length of the house.  The lower level is a luxurious retreat that can be used as a separate living space or for entertaining. There is a  spare room with additional hook up for laundry. It has  a built-in bar, beverage cooler, sink and  wine rack, with an amazing custom ceiling that outlines the space. The basement bedroom open up to a private patio. The bathroom is a Spa like Oasis with a large tiled shower that has a bench and rain shower head above and a pull out Sprayer. The sink floats above the floors and there is WiFI lights and music from the shower fan. What a fantastic space!!!!!  The floor plan can be found under the Virtual Tour.
